H3.text: The Archibald Fountain is in which Australian city. Sydney

A4.text: The Archibald Fountain is located in Hyde Park, in central Sydney.

A5.text: The fountain was unveiled on 14 March 1932 by the Lord Mayor of Sydney, Samuel Walder.
